OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fwith some late sunshine this evening.
OL,7,FMainly dry with clear spells for the
OL,8,Frest of night bringing a risk of
OL,9,Ffrost. Cloudier for the western Isles
OL,10,Ftowards dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FSunny spells and a touch of
OL,13,Ffrost first thing in the morning for
OL,14,Fsome. Turning rather cloudy through
OL,15,Fthe day, patchy rain arriving in west,
OL,16,Fbut mainly dry in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
