OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fgood deal of cloud around during this
OL,7,Fperiod with showers, perhaps some
OL,8,Flonger spells of rain on Saturday.
OL,9,FRather breezy at times.
